A '''stratablock''' was one of the 17 affluent areas of the planet [[Metellos/Legends|Metellos]] where the buildings towered more than a kilometer above the surface.

==History==
The stratablocks were surrounded on all sides by a sea of single-story structures, packed tightly together. Though Metellos was a huge [[Ecumenopolis/Legends|ecumenopolis]], most of the land area, and indeed most of its population, lived in shabby, polluted slums hugging ground level. The stratablocks stood out, "as if a chunk of [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]] had simply been dropped there."<ref name="CCW">''[[Coruscant and the Core Worlds]]''</ref>

